  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "1730ae8ca9512aa8cca68c1bd7055391509ca9ac06a73c1766a7fdbe1d9796c8": "Ah, [?]. I apologise, but I'm rather busy at the moment.",
    "ffa135701d295157b07290be8437526f8b53eaacdcd1d95718ad115ccc7fc6cc": "I'm busy, [?]. You'd better talk to Ghrim.",
    "8683862e29a726657f125a52872b575c31edd0a57ff1dbceaf01ad64fa474b3f": "I'm sorry, [?], but I'm very busy. Talk to my son and daughter if Ghrim can't help you.",
    "f2a7c861d198fee67425c2d6fa8a297a16fbe2f1cadac59648b201cc7688d9d8": "That never prevented me from ruling this kingdom when I was your age, [?].",
    "0a99e9e4b204bb14c93ed7648ef803e98977ad00fa71cd666d19b7b8cc107ada": "Have you spoken to the citizens yet, [?]?",
    "c64ead69ca881f53a5b3339aa8fca6bd8dbe9237cc3c210e5d2fdfa57c266352": "[?], go and talk to Sigrid and ask her what she thinks she's doing.",
    "082f89a59f8131321894d0e3dc60058217e04b53244da536917286d8cec1ffcf": "Perhaps not, [?].",
    "2089cee1c74137cbb999ca891954ebc77af4c0ccd9a198e40b1af7f03c8d2d42": "How are your investigations going, [?]?",
    "611019eb5e85df5be8172ea0a3b9fc1bd83eab11f7e1c928eaa999fc34a5f5e2": "In the meantime, [?], you have managed to avert a war and bring the culprits to light.",
    "0079a27828c42714dee59e74d84e31aabab5f0d9a3df806f37fa30da70620fe5": "Thank you for your work in bringing peace back to these islands, [?].",
    "993f432993bdf8786f85aec35a7e0690ccdd5032a9b9bb892b046449637ae8ac": "Hahaha! You are bold, [?], but then I have yet to see a good ruler who was not.",
    "0af8089adf93a4c55682c429610e7351bcd5f0c087ded739cc6b13b1ce7eb3d9": "How are you getting on, [?]? Have you talked to Queen Sigrid of Etceteria?",
    "ac7e76d7c3fd11f98b5d312fc7ddc32c9c9bf2d517ceddbf7e23407decb8cb5c": "How are you getting on, [?]? Have you convinced Sigrid yet?",
    "d199d7680a92c1596595a94d849b273acd620081e35a09a846f57e6db21d6b9b": "How are you getting on, [?]? Have you found me a pen yet?"
  }
}